Ninja Jump Kid - Super Fun Stick-man Run Action Game For Kids PRO is an arcade game developed by David Januszewicz. It came out on 21-03-2014. MagMedia Apps published the game.
You can play Ninja Jump Kid - Super Fun Stick-man Run Action Game For Kids PRO on iOS.
